- Use the `useForm` hook with proper configuration options
- Implement form validation using built-in validation or external libraries like Zod
- Utilize the `Controller` component for controlled inputs
- Use controlled components for better performance
- Use the watch function for real-time form state changes
- Implement custom hooks for reusable form logic
- Use the setValue function for dynamic form updates

